snippet.title: Disney GUILTY PARTY: Sleuths Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-Order at http://nku.me/pre_order_GuiltyParty 

Meet the savvy sleuths of the Dickens Detective Agency from the new mystery game, Disney Guilty Party.

IGN's "Best Family Game" winner at E3 2010. In Stores: August 31, 2010.
